*Settings*
Here you can change bot language, update subscription or add your own bot for posting.

*Current bot:* {botname}

{status}

*Set up polls*
You can enable or disable sending posts which contain polls. Also, you can add your own text to these posts.

*Current Custom text:* {now}

*Reactions*
You can configure the reactions Inline-buttons that the bot will send under the messages.

_Autoreactions_ allows to add Inline-buttons only to those posts where words that you specify.

*Important:* if you connected your own bot, reactions would not work.

